						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the entrance of the Rāmasvāmi temple in the Bazaar street.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śubhakṛit, Chaitra, ba. 30.</p>						

						<p>Settles the rates of contributions payable by the several villages of the Puṅganūru-sīma by <hi rend="italic">Tammaya-Gauṇayavāru</hi> instead of farming the revenue of the <hi rend="italic">sīma.</hi> In late characters.</p>						

						</summary>
